<center>
<table border=0 width=495>
<tr><td>
<img src="graphics/single.gif" vspace=4><br>
<p><font size=+2>W</font>elcome to the Federal Energy Management
Program (FEMP) website.  FEMP's mission is to reduce the cost of
government by advancing energy efficiency, water conservation, and
the use of solar and other renewable energy.  FEMP accomplishes its
mission by creating partnerships, leveraging resources, transferring
technology, and providing training and support. Collectively, FEMP and Federal agencies will <em><a href="bsbmtc.html">Save
Billions from Federal Energy Management.</a></em>
</td></tr></table><p><br>

<center><font size=-1><a href="aboutfmp.html">About FEMP</a> | <a href="techasst.html">Technical Assistance</a> | <a href="financing.html">Project Financing</a> | <a href="news.html">News & Events</a><br><a href="greening.html">Greening Initiatives</a> | <a href="showcase.html">Showcase Facilities</a> | <a href="http://www.arc.cmu.edu/~satish/femp/eefp.html">Federal Procurement</a></font><p>
