</dt>
</center></div>
<dd>National award winning program combining teaching principles and practicalities of energy efficiency with hands-on 
inspection of the school building to identify energy / heat leaks and inefficiencies. Solutionshave generated ignificant 
cash savings.<br>
</dd>
