<DOCHDR>
http://www.eren.doe.gov:80/pv/absorption.html 205.168.79.27 19970115045507 text/html 2251
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Wed, 15 Jan 1997 04:55:09 GMT
Server: NCSA/1.5
Content-type: text/html
Last-modified: Thu, 09 Jan 1997 21:16:44 GMT
